{"tid":1264991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[自己香港自己救]中國的人臉識別監控系統登陸香港，全港cctv發現案","createTime":"2019-06-29T03:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T09:02:57.000Z","uid":51090,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"be1e5e1ec99083dd0f5981bf51d2d4261870c6a0","tid":1264991,"uid":51090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:27:18.000Z","msg":"引用：#1混血麻鬼鬼<br />\n<br />\n&bull;&nbsp;12h<br />\n<br />\n發夢個陣有巴打一齊去拆左佢<br />\n香港本身已經好和平，我唔要比人1984咁24h監視<br />\n<br />\n係男人嘅同我出嚟，要保衛香港🇭🇰<br />\n私隱無價，自由都係無價<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XHNQ6fwMf3Y&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXHNQ6fwMf3Y%C2%A0&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=23f97af6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XHNQ6fwMf3Y&nbsp;</a><br />\n中國的人臉識別監控系統有多厲害？ - BBC News&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港示威者監控計劃率先係九龍灣/觀塘/啟德測試<br />\n￼<br />\n￼<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2323527/%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E3%80%80%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%89%8D%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E5%95%9F%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2323527%2F%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2587%2588%25E6%259F%25B1%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%2595%259F%25E7%2594%25A8&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=9bb35556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2323527/%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E3%80%80%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%89%8D%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E5%95%9F%E7%94%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n政府資訊科技總監林偉喬指，計劃目標設置約400枝智慧燈柱，約一半會視乎擺放位置安裝攝影機和探測器，所有燈柱都有藍牙感應器、燈柱地理位置二維碼和無綫射頻識別定位；除了觀塘和啟德，計劃亦會在中環／金鐘、灣仔／銅鑼灣、尖沙咀和旺角安裝智慧燈柱。<br />\n<br />\n呢枝燈柱有乜功能？<br />\n智慧燈柱上最多可安裝3個圓形外殼，以放置各種感應器和鏡頭，供政府部門收集城市數據。<br />\n<br />\n其中包括:&nbsp;<br />\nA: 無死角多角度高清攝影<br />\n-多個政府部門會在燈柱上安裝裝置，例如燈柱上部的圓型外殼內有全景攝影機<br />\n<br />\nB: RFID 配合新身份證 全天候掃描燈柱附近位置嘅人<br />\n-地政總署亦會藉無綫射頻識別(即係RFID)及燈柱地理位置二維碼<br />\n延申閱讀:<br />\nRFID<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B0%84%E9%A2%91%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B0%2584%25E9%25A2%2591%25E8%25AF%2586%25E5%2588%25AB&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=d9f330bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B0%84%E9%A2%91%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB</a><br />\n<br />\n中國平安奪eID系統合約 創科局指明年申請居屋報稅可用<br />\n平安科技中標的eID合約，價值4,400萬元，包括提供人臉識別及影像處理系統，為期8年半。資科辦表示，現正與各部門商討和制定各項電子政府服務採用eID的時間表和細節......市民在2020年中可用eID登入26項政府服務，至2021年中則增至逾110項服務。林強調，身份證和面相資料，只會在登記時儲存於政府的後台系統，政府會用「最高規格」管理，並做好滲透測試（Penetration Test），確保能抵禦攻擊，所有開發者和服務供應商不能取用數據。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190409/59469875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190409%2F59469875&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=e572fc2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190409%2F59469875&h=d11d769a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190409/59469875</a><br />\n<br />\nC: 將A,B兩項收集到嘅資料send去政府server￼<br />\n因為出街無data/人多load空氣而登入左政府wifi/Scan到你張身份證個RFID/高清拍攝/ 所得資料用5G速度去到各政府部門/後台系統&nbsp;<br />\n-集定位、Wi-Fi及5G基站功能於一身(引述晴報)<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2323786/%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E7%B4%84400%E6%94%AF%20%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2323786%2F%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%25A8%2599%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A3%259D%25E7%25B4%2584400%25E6%2594%25AF%2520%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2587%2588%25E6%259F%25B1%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=605e5a18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2323786/%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E7%B4%84400%E6%94%AF%20%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A</a><br />\n<br />\n編輯引用<br />\n我都係借人post<br />\n大家見到邊到有依種cctv就報個位置上黎<br />\n等大家發夢都小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有力出力<br />\n又有新兵種-拆彈部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf41a17dc8a0ce49eca3116643c49202df4e2ac","tid":1264991,"uid":51090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:27:41.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"d4795e1e6164aefb2298c4a364436f4313cdb1fd","tid":1264991,"uid":83251,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyAFVqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyAFVqx.jpg&h=420d6c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yiSXXDS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiSXXDS.jpg&h=e36dfc64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d83b61b483c4f720dc4a28f15e8201d6138d400b","tid":1264991,"uid":51090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4795e1e6164aefb2298c4a364436f4313cdb1fd","tid":1264991,"uid":83251,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyAFVqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyAFVqx.jpg&h=420d6c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yiSXXDS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiSXXDS.jpg&