"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"可以整個google map mark低所有新式cam既位置<br />\n將會好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:35:10.000Z","msg":"要人報料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發夢想拆彈都唔知去邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c8da8184cef9fa7e69c5275f03470086205251","tid":1264991,"uid":72083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:36:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"012d7313454d4acba85cba4e928dac9f5507b684","tid":1264991,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>2047年 中共不死香港死。<br />\n<strong>香港最寶貴唔係個島仔，最寶貴係香港人。<br />\n邊到有大量港人邊到就係香港</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開啟方舟計劃，建新香港！</span></span>作為香港既backup plan,現在需要各界精英加入<br />\n<br />\n歡迎入谷討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=e6565cb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w</a><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d3fbe831e4bee2f712f6afc5b5101e3e802fb01f","tid":1264991,"uid":51090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"012d7313454d4acba85cba4e928dac9f5507b684","tid":1264991,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>2047年 中共不死香港死。<br />\n<strong>香港最寶貴唔係個島仔，最寶貴係香港人。<br />\n邊到有大量港人邊到就係香港</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開啟方舟計劃，建新香港！</span></span>作為香港既backup plan,現在需要各界精英加入<br />\n<br />\n歡迎入谷討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft